text: František Zyka (born 3 March 1902, date of death unknown) was a Czech long- distance runner. He competed in the marathon at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Czech male long-distance runners Category:Czech male marathon runners Category:Olympic athletes of Czechoslovakia Category:Sportspeople from Prague
